dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning for Columbia County, Wisconsin in 2012. It is a feature dataset within the geodatabase, Columbia_Zoning_2012.gdb. This feature dataset includes the feature layers 'COLUMBIA_ZONING_AG_2012', and 'COLUMBIA_ZONING_BASEDISTRICTS_2012'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For most current data, please visit http://www.co.columbia.wi.us/ColumbiaCounty/landinformation/InteractiveMapping/tabid/235/Default.aspx
